  - label: UN — the justice and reconciliation process in Rwanda (primary)
    url: https://www.un.org/en/preventgenocide/rwanda/pdf/bgjustice.pdf
    archive_url: https://web.archive.org/web/20260602191016/https://www.un.org/en/preventgenocide/rwanda/pdf/bgjustice.pdf
